CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6. 1952, page 13, reads: "GOP Women - At this table were: Viola Douglas, Velmar Brown, Leoda Frank, Alma Pulliam, Mary Hunt, Mary Toy, Gladys Brown, Geneva Hamilton, Pauline Wilson and Gertrude Stokes."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including Viola Douglas, Velmar Brown, Leoda Frank, Alma Pulliam, Mary Hunt, Mary Toy, Gladys Brown, Geneva Hamilton, Pauline Wilson, and Gertrude Stokes, seated at banquet table 154 for county Republican victory celebration in Syria Mosque
